RiDDiM ~~ SHOUTcast on a diet
==============================================================

Synopsis
---------------------------------------------------------------

        % ./riddim.py -k start
        % mplayer http://localhost:18944
 

Dependencies
---------------------------------------------------------------

        % python --version
        Python 2.6.5

